# Backend Setup Guide (Node.js/Laravel + MySQL)

## 1. Database Schema & Relasi (Migration)

Pastikan tabel memiliki `ON DELETE CASCADE`.

**Laravel Migration: Siswa**
```php
Schema::create('siswas', function (Blueprint $table) {
    $table->id();
    $table->foreignId('kelas_id')->constrained('kelas')->onDelete('cascade');
    $table->string('nama');
    $table->enum('jenis_kelamin', ['L', 'P'])->nullable();
    $table->string('nisn')->nullable();
    $table->timestamps();
});
```

**Laravel Migration: Nilai**
```php
Schema::create('nilais', function (Blueprint $table) {
    $table->id();
    $table->foreignId('siswa_id')->constrained('siswas')->onDelete('cascade');
    $table->foreignId('kelas_id')->constrained('kelas')->onDelete('cascade');

    // Formatif F1-F8
    for($i=1; $i<=8; $i++) $table->integer("f$i")->default(0);
    // Sumatif S1-S5
    for($i=1; $i<=5; $i++) $table->integer("s$i")->default(0);

    $table->integer('sas_non_tes')->default(0);
    $table->integer('sas_tes')->default(0);

    // Computed Columns (Optional, can be calculated on fly)
    $table->float('nilai_akhir')->default(0);
    $table->string('huruf')->nullable();

    $table->timestamps();
});
```

**Laravel Migration: Kehadiran**
```php
Schema::create('kehadirans', function (Blueprint $table) {
    $table->id();
    $table->foreignId('siswa_id')->constrained('siswas')->onDelete('cascade');
    $table->foreignId('kelas_id')->constrained('kelas')->onDelete('cascade');
    // Menyimpan 20 pertemuan sebagai kolom JSON atau 20 kolom terpisah.
    // Disini contoh menggunakan kolom terpisah p1-p20 sesuai request "record default".
    for($i=1; $i<=20; $i++) $table->string("p$i", 1)->nullable(); 
    $table->timestamps();
});
```

